OL,3,CTwo men charged after rogue traders
OL,4,Ccharge pensioner #30,000 for roof work
OL,6,FPolice officers in Fareham who've been
OL,7,Finvestigating rogue traders have
OL,8,Fcharged two men, after a woman in her
OL,9,F80's paid over #30,000 for work on her
OL,10,Froof they said she needed.
OL,12,FThe pair were arrested when officers
OL,13,Fwent to properties in Titchfield,
OL,14,FFareham and Southampton.
