OL,6,FPaul Robert Cooper, 40, of
OL,7,FSouthfields, Fareham, and Albert
OL,8,FKempster, 30, of Southampton Road,
OL,9,FTitchfield, have both been charged
OL,10,Fwith fraud by false representation and
OL,11,Facquiring, using or possessing
OL,12,Fcriminal property.
OL,14,FAs part of their nvestigation, two
OL,15,Fother men were arrested, but they've
OL,16,Fboth been bailed while enquiries
OL,17,Fcontinue.
