OL,4,Ccharge pensioner #30,000 for roof work
OL,6,FIt was reported to police that on
OL,7,Fapproximately 7 occasions (between 27
OL,8,FSeptember - 17 October) a woman in her
OL,9,F80s was visited at her home by men
OL,10,Fpurporting to be tradesmen, who told
OL,11,Fher she needed roof work doing.
OL,13,FMinimal work was completed by these
OL,14,Fmen on each visit, and the victim paid
OL,15,F#32,800 to the men.
OL,17,FArrests made:
