OL,4,Ccharge pensioner #30,000 for roof work
OL,6,FChief Inspector Marcus Kennedy,
OL,7,FDistrict Commander for Policing in
OL,8,FFareham & Gosport, said: "Doorstep
OL,9,Fcrime is a nasty offence type which
OL,10,Fsees some of the most vulnerable
OL,11,Fmembers of our community exploited,
OL,12,Fmanipulated or intimidated into
OL,13,Fparting with enormous sums of cash.
OL,15,F"There is no place for it, and I hope
OL,16,Ftoday's activity sends a message that
OL,17,Fwe will take any reports of this type
OL,18,Fof crime seriously and we will act.
